headline: Western Digital (WDC) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of leading data storage manufacturer Western Digital (NASDAQ: WDC) jumped 4% in the morning session after Cantor Fitzgerald nearly doubled its price target on the stock to $160 from $85, while maintaining an Overweight rating.
